{"tid":1752294,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"政府想靠搞區選嚟用民意去止暴制亂就落錯注","createTime":"2019-11-24T19:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T01:28:41.000Z","uid":58998,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"993ac6fbe081e3fae2c7e34808401145f2fd14b8","tid":1752294,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:40:24.000Z","msg":"笑死人，如果政府預計到輸成咁，根本無可能會搞區選，中央都唔會俾佢搞嚟出醜<br />\n佢搞得，就只會係預料建制一定贏，最少係六四咁贏，甚至民意倒戈，可以贏更多<br />\n但結果係齋計票數，我地都佔咗六成，計議席嘅佢更加輸到差啲滅門<br />\n惟一解釋就係政府完全錯估民意，但佢本身應該係有最多人力同資源去評估民意，好可能係佢樓下全部刷鞋仔，無人講真話<br />\n<br />\n而最大問題係政府仲好可能之前隱瞞埋中共，將民意倒轉嚟講，今次無得再呃，我真心唔知林鄭可以點解釋"},{"pid":"bac0aacca5dbfd7e191def46e1b045ad9063b4ef","tid":1752294,"uid":96182,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:44:45.000Z","msg":"幫佢諗埋仲有沉默400萬冇得投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d785bef45bc4582bae9237016c4a39abc82a72","tid":1752294,"uid":58998,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bac0aacca5dbfd7e191def46e1b045ad9063b4ef","tid":1752294,"uid":96182,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:44:45.000Z","msg":"幫佢諗埋仲有沉默400萬冇得投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:48:35.000Z","msg":"睇埋1至17歲佢咪輸得仲撚金"},{"pid":"1da5704337efdfdc245dbb2e8c5cfc3ac6deaad5","tid":1752294,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:48:54.000Z","msg":"今日連登風向: 恥笑建制，沉醉勝利，營造和勇之別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1752189\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1752189</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">SAVE POLYU</span></span>"},{"pid":"5aad8d908445c3fc4a906aeb7c3e043a4fc77478","tid":1752294,"uid":35613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:50:04.000Z","msg":"懷疑D沉默大多數一晚死晒"},{"pid":"d1eb3d56bfa388368792360f885ba44c461296bd","tid":1752294,"uid":51349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73d785bef45bc4582bae923